    {
      "text": "Airforce Delta (エアフォース デルタ), known as Deadly Skies in Europe, is a series of combat flight simulation games developed and published by Konami. The series began in 1999 with Airforce Delta for Dreamcast, with its last main series game being the 2004 Airforce Delta Strike.\nThe series has been compared to Ace Combat in its gameplay.",
